state's congressional delegation. In the 1st District, Republican
Bernalillo County District Attorney Steve Schiff had the edge over
Democrat Tom Udall, nephew of Arizona Rep. Morris Udall, to succeed
retiring 10-term Republican Manuel Lujan Jr.
